//ðŸ’» Question 5
        int  c = 10;
        int  d = c--;
        System.out.println(c);
        System.out.println(d);
ðŸ§  Answer:
        c = 9
        d = 10

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

//ðŸ’» Question 6
        int  c = 10;
        int  d = --c;
        System.out.println(c);
        System.out.println(d);
ðŸ§  Answer:
        c = 9
        d = 9

